                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/6500" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9531 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“护身符”还是“催命符”：堂堂所的双层“抽屉协议”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Amulet” or “Death Amulet”: Analysis of the Double-layer “Drawer Agreement”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">颜恩点，吴迪，陆晓璐，孙锦文，于晓宇</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学管理学院</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">堂堂会计师事务所</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公共关系/外事部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">抽屉协议；新《证券法》；中小会计师事务所；审计风险；2022百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"> Drawer Agreements; New Securities Law; Small and Medium Accounting Firms; Audit risk</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“ST公司审计专业户”堂堂所因双层“抽屉协议”获A股史上最贵罚单，引发社会广泛关注。新《证券法》背景下，越来越多中小会计师事务所通过承接ST公司审计业务来进入高收入的证券服务领域。由于ST公司经营状况复杂，中小会计师事务所承接此类业务面临诸多挑战。本案例围绕堂堂所签订的双层“抽屉协议”的具体内容，主要介绍了签订协议的背景、受证监会的处罚结果以及堂堂所“喊冤”的全部过程。本案例旨在让学员理解“抽屉协议”对中小会计师事务所带来的正反两方面的影响，并启发学员掌握帮助中小会计师事务所有效降低高审计风险的现代风险导向审计模型和三种有效手段。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all"> “ST Company Audit Professional Institution” Tangtang received the most expensive fine in the history of A-shares due to double-layer “drawer agreement”, which has aroused widespread concern in the society. Under the background of new “Securities Law”, more and more small and medium-sized accounting firms have entered the high-income securities service field by undertaking the audit business of ST companies. Due to the complex operating conditions of ST companies, small and medium-sized accounting firms are faced with many challenges in undertaking such businesses. This case focuses on the specific content of the double-layer “drawer agreement”signed by Tangtang, and mainly introduces the background of signing the agreement, the punishment result of the CSRC, and the whole process of “calling grievances” for Tangtang. This case aims to let students understand the positive and negative impact of the “drawer agreement” on small and medium accounting firms, and inspire students to master the modern risk-oriented audit model and three effective audit models that help small and medium accounting firms to effectively reduce high audit risks. means.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《审计理论与实务》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">信息不对称理论；现代风险导向审计理论；审计基本要求；审计质量；抽屉协议；审计业务约定书；审计独立性；审计质量与控制；审计职业道德规范与商业伦理</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2022-09</td>
                            </tr>
